ws):**\n\n```powershell\n$env:DB_URL = \"jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/ehs?useSSL=false&serverTimezone=UTC\"\n$env:DB_USER = \"ehs\"\n$env:DB_PASS = \"ehs\"\n```\n\n**bash/zsh (macOS/Linux):**\n\n```bash\nexport DB_URL=\"jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/ehs?useSSL=false&serverTimezone=UTC\"\nexport DB_USER=\"ehs\"\nexport DB_PASS=\"ehs\"\n```\n\n## Run the backend\n\nFrom `backend/`:\n\n```bash\nmvn spring-boot:run\n```\n\nThe API starts on <http://localhost:8080> (context path `/`). On startup it\nconnects to MySQL and runs Flyway migrations.\n\nTo build a jar:\n\n```bash\nmvn -DskipTests package\n```\n\n## Run the frontend\n\nFrom `frontend/`:\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n```\n\nThe Vite dev server serves the app on <http://localhost:5173> and proxies any\n`/api/*` request to the backend at <http://localhost:8080>.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}}
